Package: clrng
Version: 0.1
Date: 2019-09-14
Title: Random numbers on the gpu
Author: Ruoyong Xu, Patrick Brown
Description: Tools for generating random numbers on GPU's. The package builds on gpuR to provide facilities to generate random numbers on a GPU and save the results as R objects
